Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 12), python2.7

Package: xva-tool
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python2.7 (>= 2.7.5)
Description: Advanced Zero-Copy Streaming Core Engine for XenServer
 An enterprise-grade standalone utility designed by Alexander Maassen. 
 Extracts and flattens XenServer XVA/OVA image streams into flat raw disk 
 structures using a pure, zero-dependency Python 2.7 framework core.
 Requires a full Python standard library layout with hashlib support.
